quest.name: Waiting to Inhale
journal: The moogle on the watchtower is cradling her rumbling tummy.
It is almost time for a change in shift, and this poor moogle's replacement is nowhere to be found. Slay four tulihands to secure a safe path and ensure the moogle on the watchtower does not starve.
You have slain the tulihands, and now the shift replacement should be able to report to duty safely. Deliver the good news to the hungry moogle.
The on duty moogle hurries home after hearing your report, eager to get her hands on some kupo nuts.
objectives: Report to the moogle on lookout duty.

dialogue.name: MONITORINGMOG01835
dialogue.text: Whatever can be taking her so long, kupo? My replacement should've been here already, but I don't see her anywhere. I'm so hungry... I wager she went home on account of those troublesome tulihands that're flapping about.

dialogue.name: MONITORINGMOG01835
dialogue.text: If you slay four of them that should secure a safe path, giving my replacement no excuse. Please, my stomach begs you, kupo!

dialogue.name: MONITORINGMOG01835
dialogue.text: I can't go on, I need some kupo nuts... Adventurer, please slay the tulihands for me!

dialogue.name: MONITORINGMOG01835
dialogue.text: Thank you! Now that the tulihands are out of the way, it's only a matter of time before my replacement gets here! I'm about to pass out from hunger, so I think I'll go ahead. What could go wrong, kupo?
